    "rich_text_q4ed7V": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_block_YrcCYz": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Sustainable Seamless Bikinis for All-Day Comfort and Style",
            "title_heading": true,
            "accordion_enabled": true,
            "text": "<p>Our seamless bikinis are proof that you don’t have to choose between style, comfort, and performance. Designed for women who live in and around the water, each piece blends a flattering fit with a barely-there feel — so you can focus on the moment, not on adjusting your swimwear.</p><p>At Ocean Soul Swimwear, we craft every women’s seamless bikini from luxurious Italian recycled fabric, chosen for its softness, durability, and eco-friendly credentials. The seamless construction means no digging, rubbing, or harsh edges — just smooth lines and a sculpted silhouette that feels as good as it looks.</p><p>Perfect for everything from surf sessions to sunbathing, our seamless bikinis are made with UPF 50+ sun protection to shield your skin from harmful UV rays. They’re double-lined for support and coverage, so you can swim, paddle, or stretch on the sand with total confidence.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "center": true,
            "block_width": 100,
            "accordion_icon_color": "#000000",
            "accordion_icon_size": 20
          }
