    "image_with_text_mxD9Td": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/The_Banyak_Bikini_in_Black_ocean_soul_bali.jpg",
        "image_position": "right",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 450,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Ocean Soul Swimwear’s Signature Seamless Design",
        "text": "<p>Our seamless bikinis are more than just stitch-free — they’re carefully engineered for fit, function, and longevity.</p><p><strong>Premium Italian Recycled Fabric:</strong> Soft, breathable, and highly durable against salt, chlorine, and sun exposure.<br/></p><p><strong>UPF 50+ Sun Protection:</strong> Built-in skin protection for peace of mind during long days outdoors.<br/></p><p><strong>Double-Lined Support:</strong> Ensures your bikini stays opaque, even when wet, while offering a gentle, secure hold.<br/></p><p><strong>Ethical Production:</strong> Handmade in Bali in small batches to minimise waste and overproduction.<br/></p><p><strong>Mix & Match Options:</strong> Pair tops and bottoms your way for a bikini set that’s uniquely yours.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_387Ymp": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/tripseatravellers5_1ebc5ad4-4707-445b-bcb3-68531e160fe5.jpg",
        "image_position": "left",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 400,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Why Choose a Seamless Bikini?",
        "text": "<h3></h3><p>Once you try a seamless bikini, it’s hard to go back to anything else. The absence of bulky seams means:</p><p>No Digging or Pinching – Smooth edges prevent discomfort and red marks.<br/></p><p>Flattering, Sleek Look – Seamless construction sits flush against the skin for a sculpted shape.<br/></p><p>Lightweight Comfort – Feels barely there, even after hours in or out of the water.<br/></p><p>This makes them ideal for active water sports like surfing, paddle boarding, and swimming — as well as long, lazy beach days.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_AHN6V4": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/The_Bali_Bikini_pink_Seamless_swimwear.jpg",
        "image_position": "right",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 450,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "Performance Meets Lifestyle",
        "text": "<p>We design our sustainable seamless bikinis for real women who move, play, and live in their swimwear. That means:</p><p><strong>Surf-Tested:</strong> Tops and bottoms that stay in place through duck dives, wipeouts, and paddle-outs.<br/></p><p><strong>Quick-Drying:</strong> Go from beach to café without feeling damp or uncomfortable.<br/></p><p><strong>Fade & Stretch Resistant:</strong> Colours and fit stay true season after season.<br/></p><p>Whether you’re packing for a tropical getaway or chasing summer at home, your seamless bikini will be ready for it all.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
    "image_with_text_hAKVKW": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "name": "Image with text",
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Triangle_string_bikini_green.png",
        "image_position": "left",
        "image_size": "medium",
        "image_height": "fixed",
        "desktop_image_height": 450,
        "mobile_image_height": 450,
        "title": "How to Style Your Seamless Bikini",
        "text": "<h3></h3><p>One of the best things about seamless bikinis is their versatility. Here are some ways to make yours work harder:</p><p>Beach to Brunch: Throw on a linen shirt or breezy sarong over your bikini for an effortless transition to streetwear.<br/></p><p>Active Days: Layer under a women’s rash vest for extra sun protection without sacrificing comfort.<br/></p><p>Mix & Match: Pair a bold top with neutral bottoms (or vice versa) for a personalised look that’s always fresh.</p>",
        "button_text": "Button",
        "link": "",
        "center_align": true,
        "text_color": "#606060",
        "background_color": "#f7f7f7"
      }
    },
