    "rich_text_yqr4bA": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_block_Ne7Dei": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Fit for Every Body",
            "title_heading": true,
            "accordion_enabled": false,
            "text": "<p>Our seamless bikinis are designed to move with you — no matter your body shape. With adjustable ties, stretchy fabric, and carefully considered cuts, they adapt to your curves without restriction.</p><p>From sleek black seamless bikinis to vibrant seasonal shades, our range has something for every style. Whichever you choose, you’ll enjoy:</p><p>- A flattering, comfortable fit you’ll want to wear all day<br/>- Premium, eco-friendly materials that last<br/>- Ethical craftsmanship you can be proud of<br/></p><p>Ocean Soul Swimwear’s seamless bikinis are where style, comfort, and sustainability meet. Explore the collection today and find your new favourite bikini.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "center": true,
            "block_width": 100,
            "accordion_icon_color": "#000000",
            "accordion_icon_size": 20
          }
        }
      },
