    "image_with_text_overlay_aE4dNT": {
      "type": "image-with-text-overlay",
      "name": "Image with text overlay",
      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/The_Aceh_Midnight_Rash_vest_and_bikini.jpg",
        "overlay": false,
        "background_attachment": "fixed",
        "height": 400,
        "mobile_height": 400,
        "text_align": "center",
        "caption_vertical": 50,
        "caption_horizontal": 50,
        "heading": "",
        "subheading_text": "<h3>A Sustainable Choice for the Planet</h3><p>Every eco-friendly seamless bikini in this collection is made from ECONYL® regenerated nylon, crafted from ocean waste like discarded fishing nets and fabric scraps. By choosing one, you’re helping to reduce marine pollution and support the shift towards circular fashion.</p><p>We produce in small batches to ensure quality and avoid unnecessary waste, and every piece is sewn by skilled artisans who are paid fairly for their work. This is swimwear you can feel good about wearing — in every sense.</p>",
